    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■新赛季资讯</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >‧新侵略者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SEASON 9由「沙鲁＆沙鲁二世」、「魔人普乌（吸收孙悟饭）」、「布罗利（Z）」等3名新侵略者登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧「沙鲁＆沙鲁二世」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新侵略者「沙鲁＆沙鲁二世」登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要使用新技能「去吧！沙鲁二世们」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就可以将沙鲁二世们召唤至场景中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过沙鲁及沙鲁二世们绝佳的合作，将幸存者逼上绝境吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧「魔人普乌（吸收孙悟饭）」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新侵略者「魔人普乌（吸收孙悟饭）」登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在等级3的状态下达成特定条件后，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就可以进化为「魔人普乌（吸收孙悟饭）」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来使用新型态及新技能「超级恶鬼神风特攻术」等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与既有的「魔人普乌」截然不同的战斗方式攻击幸存者吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧「布罗利（Z）」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「布罗利（Z）」终于登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本新侵略者可以在进化等级2或3进化至等级4！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择想要尽快分出胜负的等级2，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或在下半场后以强大实力压制的等级3吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦进化至等级4后，就可以用恐怖的实力蹂躏幸存者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这股力量宛如「恶魔」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加3名新侵略者，内容丰富的SEASON 9！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来使用新侵略者的实力，将幸存者一网打尽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/5f971e05ab5dd84372cbbccbc4fa8277.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※各赛季追加的侵略者及幸存者造型需于游戏内解锁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >献给战斗力5的你们──终极脱逃剧！！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1名强敌对上7名普通市民！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验七龙珠才具备的「相距悬殊的战力差距」！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■关于本作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《七龙珠 破界斗士》为1对7的线上非对称动作游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由七龙珠最具代表性的敌对角色弗力札、布罗利等「侵略者」，与7名不具超凡力量的普通市民「幸存者」间展开的终极脱逃游戏！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■幸存者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/0b1a174b9cde73df9240c116e4867719.poster.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/0b1a174b9cde73df9240c116e4867719.webm?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/0b1a174b9cde73df9240c116e4867719.mp4?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>・从封闭空间「时空裂痕」脱逃吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请和伙伴们同心协力，有效使用各种手段排除侵略者，从战场中脱逃！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・使用多样化的方式对抗，并活下去吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快使用龙珠雷达、太阳拳或瞬间移动等等七龙珠系列最广为人知的道具及招式吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时还能借用超级战士的力量暂时变身，与侵略者对打！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且收齐7颗龙珠召唤出神龙的话，威力还能更上一层楼！说不定还能打倒侵略者……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/f60f6af4b6f64a6fefd0e0e2af0adc21.poster.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/f60f6af4b6f64a6fefd0e0e2af0adc21.webm?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/f60f6af4b6f64a6fefd0e0e2af0adc21.mp4?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/9fc46801cdd98297bd3cc7e5f1023830.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=231 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■侵略者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/b99f99f656bb3ff135a72ea21c826616.poster.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/b99f99f656bb3ff135a72ea21c826616.webm?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/b99f99f656bb3ff135a72ea21c826616.mp4?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>・别放过任何幸存者！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现七龙珠故事中压倒性的实力，阻止7名幸存者逃离战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >歼灭所有幸存者，大获全胜吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/68c268b4fe04a625f15c651c9f6a817b.poster.avif?t=1762511713\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/68c268b4fe04a625f15c651c9f6a817b.webm?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276760/extras/68c268b4fe04a625f15c651c9f6a817b.mp4?t=1762511713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>・透过进化变得更凶狠！！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >侵略者透过不断进化，会变得愈来愈强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请多多袭击幸存者及民众，吸收他们的能源吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，每次进化还会强化侵略者的必杀技及技能喔！只要进化到最后阶段，就可以施展最强的必杀技……！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■个人化要素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・侵略者、幸存者各自都有技能、造型等个人化元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情享受属于自己的个人化造型吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※各赛季中新增的侵略者或幸存者造型需先在游戏内解锁，方能使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※本游戏为在线专用软体，离线中无法游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※本作主要为玩家间的「在线多人游玩」游戏。单人游玩模式下仅可游玩简单的教学、包含世界观说明的「故事」及学习战斗的「演练」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※在线多人游玩模式下，可与世界各地的人一同游乐。系统会依据游玩区域将网络联机状态最适切的对象配对为对战对手。</p>",
